             was indicted for that <rs id="t18130113-71-off410" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130113-71-off410" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130113-71-off410" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               he, on the <rs id="t18130113-71-cd411" type="crimeDate">17th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-71-off410 t18130113-71-cd411"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-71-off413 t18130113-71-cd411"></join>, being in the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130113-71-victim676" type="victimName">
                           Martha 
                           Griffiths
                        <interp inst="t18130113-71-victim676" type="surname" value="Griffiths"></interp>
