                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-71-defend674 t18130113-71-punish416"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 23.</p>
               <p>TREADAWAY, <rs id="t18130113-71-verdict417" type="verdictDescription">
